\v 1 Happy is the husband of a good wife;
\q1 And the number of his days will be doubled.
\q1
\v 2 A brave woman rejoices her husband;
\q1 And he will fulfill his years in peace.
\q1
\v 3 A good wife is a good portion:
\q1 She will be given in the portion of such as fear the Lord.
